WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.480
wa aqoolu fil qur'ani ma jaat bihi ayatuhu fahuwa al-kareemul munzalu

00:00:09.480 --> 00:00:18.800
wa aqoolu qalallahu jalla jalaluhu wal-mustafah al-hadi walaa at-awwalu

00:00:18.800 --> 00:00:26.240
alhamdulillahi rabbil alameen, lahul hamdul hasan wa al-thana wal-jameel wa ashadu an la ilaha illa allahu wahdahu la sharika lah

00:00:26.240 --> 00:00:30.720
yaqulu al-haqqa wa hua yuhdi al-sabeel wa ashadu anna Muhammadan abduhu wa rasuluhu

00:00:30.720 --> 00:00:37.120
sallallahu alihi wa ala alihi wa ashabihi wa attabi'ina lahum bi ihsanin ila yawm al-deen amma ba'd

00:00:37.120 --> 00:00:47.120
insha'Allah wa ta'ala today we're going to start a series in which I will be speaking about the life and the biography of the 10 that were promised Jannah

00:00:47.120 --> 00:00:55.840
In Jannah insha'Allah wa ta'ala I'm going to start with Abu Bakr al-Siddiq radiAllahu ta'ala anhu

00:00:55.840 --> 00:01:00.560
Abu Bakr al-Siddiq is khalifatu rasulillahi sallallahu alayhi wa sallamah

00:01:00.560 --> 00:01:05.280
When the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallamah died he took over

00:01:05.280 --> 00:01:10.800
He was the successor of the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallam and his name is Abdullah

00:01:10.800 --> 00:01:28.720
And some of the scholars they said his name is Atiq ibn Abi Quhafah, Uthman ibn Aamir, ibn Aamir, ibn Ka'ab, ibn Sa'ad, ibn Taymi, ibn Murrah, ibn Ka'ab, ibn Luayn al-Qurashi al-Taymiyyu radiAllahu ta'ala anhu

00:01:28.720 --> 00:01:30.960
That's his full name

00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:38.480
He meets the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallamah in Taymi ibn Murrah that's where they come together him and the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallamah

00:01:38.480 --> 00:01:41.920
He died a year 13 Hijriya

00:01:41.920 --> 00:01:44.160
That's when he passed away and he died

00:01:44.160 --> 00:01:47.120
radiAllahu ta'ala anhu

00:01:47.120 --> 00:01:52.000
His daughter Aisha radiAllahu ta'ala anha she said

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:54.880
Ismuhu alladhi sammahu ahluhu bihi

00:01:54.880 --> 00:01:59.360
The name in which his family called him is Abdullahi

00:01:59.360 --> 00:02:02.960
This is his actual name

00:02:02.960 --> 00:02:08.160
And I've taken upon myself a few years back

00:02:08.160 --> 00:02:10.960
Just to test a lot of people with the name of Abu Bakr

00:02:10.960 --> 00:02:12.560
I asked them

00:02:12.560 --> 00:02:14.320
I said to them

00:02:14.320 --> 00:02:17.120
What's the name of Abu Bakr?

00:02:17.120 --> 00:02:22.320
And everybody or a lot of those who I asked they said Abu Bakr, Abu Bakr, Abu Bakr

00:02:22.320 --> 00:02:26.960
And some said I don't know I thought his name was Abu Bakr

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:29.760
No his name is actually Abdullahi

00:02:29.760 --> 00:02:34.800
And some scholars believe his name is Ateeq

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:37.600
Aisha said Ismuhu alladhi sammahu ahluhu bihi Abdullahi

00:02:37.600 --> 00:02:40.640
The name that his family called him is Abdullahi

00:02:40.640 --> 00:02:46.880
But this name Ateeq overtook Abdullahi

00:02:46.880 --> 00:02:49.360
But his actual name is Abdullahi

00:02:49.360 --> 00:02:50.720
Okay

00:02:50.720 --> 00:02:54.000
And brothers and sisters it's very important Wallahi brothers

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:58.240
That we don't dismiss the biography and the life of these great Imams

00:02:58.240 --> 00:02:59.520
These great individuals

00:02:59.520 --> 00:03:00.880
These great personalities

00:03:00.880 --> 00:03:02.320
Abu Bakr, al-Siddiq

00:03:02.320 --> 00:03:04.800
The great scholar of this Ummah

00:03:04.800 --> 00:03:08.240
The great companion of the Prophet, alayhi salatu was salam

00:03:08.240 --> 00:03:10.720
It's really embarrassing that we don't know his name

00:03:10.720 --> 00:03:11.920
We don't know his biography

00:03:11.920 --> 00:03:14.240
We don't know who he was

00:03:14.240 --> 00:03:17.440
RadhiAllahu ta'ala anhu

00:03:17.440 --> 00:03:20.320
Ibn Abi Mulaika and other than him they said

00:03:20.320 --> 00:03:23.040
Innama kana Ateeq laqabal lahoo

00:03:23.040 --> 00:03:25.200
That Ateeq is actually not his name

00:03:25.200 --> 00:03:29.760
His name is actually Abdullahi

00:03:29.760 --> 00:03:33.120
But his nickname is Ateeq

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:35.440
So there's two views when it comes to Ateeq

00:03:35.440 --> 00:03:40.160
Some scholars they mention his name is Ateeq

00:03:40.160 --> 00:03:43.200
And some scholars they mention no Ateeq is a nickname of his

00:03:43.200 --> 00:03:45.520
His real name is Abdullahi

00:03:45.520 --> 00:03:47.120
Yahaib ibn Ma'inin he said

00:03:47.120 --> 00:03:49.920
Laqabuhu Ateeq

00:03:49.920 --> 00:03:51.760
His nickname is Ateeq

00:03:51.760 --> 00:03:54.720
So the question here is why was he called Ateeq?

00:03:54.720 --> 00:03:55.680
Yahaib ibn Ma'inin he said

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:58.320
li anna wajhahu kana jameela

00:03:58.320 --> 00:04:01.440
The reason is because his face was very beautiful

00:04:01.440 --> 00:04:03.520
Abu Bakr was a very handsome individual

00:04:03.520 --> 00:04:04.880
RadhiAllahu ta'ala anhu

00:04:04.880 --> 00:04:06.400
And that's why he was called

00:04:06.400 --> 00:04:07.760
Ibn Al-Arabi he said

00:04:07.760 --> 00:04:09.440
Al-Arabu taqoolu li shay'i

00:04:09.440 --> 00:04:11.760
Idha balaghan nihayata fil jawda

00:04:11.760 --> 00:04:12.960
Ateeq

00:04:12.960 --> 00:04:15.040
Ibn Al-Arabi he said

00:04:15.040 --> 00:04:21.790
That the Arabs when something reaches its fullest

00:04:21.790 --> 00:04:27.790
When something reaches its complete version

00:04:27.790 --> 00:04:29.710
In terms of its authenticity

00:04:29.710 --> 00:04:32.910
And in terms of its purity and beauty

00:04:32.910 --> 00:04:34.670
They call it Ateeq

00:04:34.670 --> 00:04:37.630
And that's why he was called Ateeq

00:04:37.630 --> 00:04:39.790
Abu Bakr radhiAllahu ta'ala anhu

00:04:39.790 --> 00:04:42.430
He was awwala man aamana min al-rijali

00:04:42.430 --> 00:04:43.630
He was the first

00:04:43.630 --> 00:04:45.630
Wa kana radhiAllahu ta'ala anhu

00:04:45.630 --> 00:04:47.310
Awwala man aamana min al-rijali

00:04:47.310 --> 00:04:50.510
He was the first to believe from the men

00:04:50.510 --> 00:04:54.030
There was no man that believed in the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:04:54.030 --> 00:04:56.590
Before Abu Bakr

00:04:56.590 --> 00:04:58.510
Wa aslama abawahu

00:04:58.510 --> 00:05:02.910
Abu Bakr his father and his mother both took Islam

00:05:02.910 --> 00:05:05.870
Aisha radhiAllahu ta'ala anhu she said

00:05:05.870 --> 00:05:10.670
Ma aslama abawa ahadi min al muhajireena illa Abu Bakr

00:05:10.670 --> 00:05:14.910
From the muhajireen no one's

00:05:14.910 --> 00:05:16.910
No one from the muhajireen

00:05:16.910 --> 00:05:20.910
Whose two parents

00:05:20.910 --> 00:05:23.310
Became Muslims other than Abu Bakr

00:05:23.310 --> 00:05:26.990
Abu Bakr was the only muhajir

00:05:27.150 --> 00:05:32.980
Whose two parents took Islam

00:05:32.980 --> 00:05:35.540
Abu Bakr radhiAllahu anhu

00:05:35.540 --> 00:05:40.100
Kana abya dh naheefan lateefan khafeefan aaridayni

00:05:40.100 --> 00:05:45.380
Yaq dhibu shaybahu bil hinnayi wal katam

00:05:45.380 --> 00:05:47.780
Abu Bakr was white

00:05:47.780 --> 00:05:48.580
And he was very skinny

00:05:48.580 --> 00:05:51.140
Naheef means he was skinny

00:05:51.140 --> 00:05:53.140
RadhiAllahu ta'ala anhu

00:05:53.140 --> 00:05:55.700
He also was khafeefan aaridayni

00:05:55.700 --> 00:05:57.540
The two sides of his bed

00:05:57.860 --> 00:06:01.140
Alid is the side of your bed was very thin

00:06:01.140 --> 00:06:03.380
He didn't have thick hair very thin

00:06:04.660 --> 00:06:06.420
Also he had some white hair

