00:06:11.300 --> 00:06:14.100
Abu Bakr radhiAllahu ta'ala anhu

00:06:14.100 --> 00:06:15.860
And that's something brothers and sisters

00:06:16.820 --> 00:06:19.220
That his father was instructed by the prophet

00:06:19.220 --> 00:06:22.460
Alayhi sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:06:22.460 --> 00:06:24.460
Abu Bakr he brought his father

00:06:24.460 --> 00:06:25.580
Abiy Quhafa

00:06:25.580 --> 00:06:27.340
Uthman ibn Abiy Quhafa

00:06:27.340 --> 00:06:29.740
He brought him to Nabilah Muhammad

00:06:29.740 --> 00:06:33.740
Remember when Abu Bakr brought his father

00:06:34.540 --> 00:06:36.140
To the prophet Alayhi sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:06:36.860 --> 00:06:38.860
And the prophet Alayhi sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:06:38.860 --> 00:06:41.500
He saw Abiy Quhafa

00:06:42.380 --> 00:06:44.300
His bed was completely white

00:06:45.820 --> 00:06:47.660
And the prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:06:48.620 --> 00:06:50.300
He said to Abiy Quhafa

00:06:52.380 --> 00:06:53.660
He said ghaiyyil shayb

00:06:54.620 --> 00:06:58.780
Ya'ni alter and change your gray hair

00:06:59.820 --> 00:07:00.380
Change it

00:07:01.260 --> 00:07:01.660
Okay

00:07:02.380 --> 00:07:03.500
Or your white hair

00:07:03.500 --> 00:07:03.980
Change it

00:07:04.620 --> 00:07:05.980
And the prophet said to him

00:07:05.980 --> 00:07:07.260
Wajitani bis sawada

00:07:07.260 --> 00:07:08.780
And stay away from using black

00:07:10.460 --> 00:07:13.100
And stay away from using black

00:07:13.100 --> 00:07:16.300
So Abu Bakr radhiAllahu anhu did the same

00:07:17.020 --> 00:07:20.780
And he used to place on those white parts of his bed

00:07:20.780 --> 00:07:22.780
He would place hinnah on it

00:07:22.860 --> 00:07:24.060
RadhiAllahu ta'ala anhu

00:07:24.620 --> 00:07:25.820
Urwa ibn al-Zubayr

00:07:27.340 --> 00:07:27.900
He said

00:07:29.100 --> 00:07:30.300
Aslama Abu Bakr

00:07:30.300 --> 00:07:31.500
Urwa ibn al-Zubayr by the way

00:07:32.380 --> 00:07:34.540
His mother is who?

00:07:36.540 --> 00:07:37.500
Asma binti Abi Bakr

00:07:39.500 --> 00:07:40.460
Urwa ibn al-Zubayr

00:07:41.180 --> 00:07:43.660
His mother is Asma binti Abi Bakr

00:07:43.660 --> 00:07:45.980
And Asma binti Abi Bakr is the daughter of Abi Bakr

00:07:46.780 --> 00:07:48.860
Urwa ibn al-Zubayr ibn Awam was married to who?

00:07:50.380 --> 00:07:53.020
Zubayr ibn Awam was married to Asma binti Abi Bakr

00:07:54.460 --> 00:07:55.260
Zubayr ibn Awam

00:07:55.900 --> 00:07:56.540
Okay

00:07:56.540 --> 00:07:57.340
He was married to who?

00:07:58.780 --> 00:08:01.900
He was married to Asma binti Abi Bakr

00:08:03.500 --> 00:08:07.180
And Zubayr ibn Awam's mother was who?

00:08:07.180 --> 00:08:08.780
Safiyah binti Abdul Muttalib

00:08:10.460 --> 00:08:16.460
As Zubayr ibn Awam's mother was Safiyah binti Abdul Muttalib

00:08:16.460 --> 00:08:17.580
Who is the prophet's what?

00:08:17.580 --> 00:08:17.980
Aunty

00:08:19.100 --> 00:08:22.060
So you can see the relationship

00:08:23.020 --> 00:08:28.940
Here between the prophet's family and Abu Bakr's family at a very early stage

00:08:29.980 --> 00:08:32.220
How they were connected and they were close to one another

00:08:34.190 --> 00:08:37.870
And the prophet of course sallallahu alayhi wa sallam married the daughter of Abu Bakr

00:08:38.430 --> 00:08:40.750
Aisha radiallahu ta'ala anha

00:08:40.750 --> 00:08:43.070
And that again strengthened the bond between the two of them

00:08:43.870 --> 00:08:46.910
So Urwa ibn al-Zubayr used to enter onto his aunty Aisha

00:08:46.910 --> 00:08:48.590
That's his maternal aunty right?

00:08:48.590 --> 00:08:50.110
So he used to enter onto her

00:08:50.110 --> 00:08:52.670
And he knew a lot about his granddad

00:08:52.670 --> 00:08:53.710
Urwa ibn al-Zubayr

00:08:53.710 --> 00:08:54.990
He would know a lot about his granddad

00:08:55.710 --> 00:08:56.190
So he said

00:08:57.630 --> 00:08:59.150
He said Abu Bakr took Islam

00:09:01.950 --> 00:09:03.390
The day in which he took Islam

00:09:06.030 --> 00:09:08.590
Abu Bakr took Islam the day he took Islam

00:09:08.590 --> 00:09:11.630
And he had 40,000 dinar

00:09:11.630 --> 00:09:22.590
And it was mentioned that Abu Bakr radiallahu ta'ala

00:09:22.590 --> 00:09:23.710
And he was a businessman

00:09:23.710 --> 00:09:28.750
So he traded and he made business to Busra in Sham more than once

00:09:29.550 --> 00:09:30.910
And it was also mentioned

00:09:30.910 --> 00:09:34.110
And he spent his money on the prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:09:34.110 --> 00:09:35.470
And for the sake of Allah

00:09:37.150 --> 00:09:39.790
So what Urwa ibn al-Zubayr is trying to say is that

00:09:39.790 --> 00:09:44.270
Abu Bakr he had 40,000 dinar

00:09:44.270 --> 00:09:47.470
Brothers and sisters dinar is thousands of dollars

00:09:48.750 --> 00:09:49.550
A lot of money

00:09:50.510 --> 00:09:52.510
Abu Bakr was wealthy, extremely wealthy

00:09:54.270 --> 00:09:55.310
And again he was a trader

00:09:55.310 --> 00:09:56.430
He was a businessman

00:09:56.430 --> 00:09:59.550
He used to go to Busra buy products and sell them and etc

00:10:02.590 --> 00:10:04.910
And what did he do with his wealth that he had?

00:10:04.910 --> 00:10:06.430
He gave all of it

00:10:07.390 --> 00:10:08.910
To the prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:10:08.910 --> 00:10:10.110
And in the cause of this religion

00:10:11.710 --> 00:10:13.150
The prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:10:13.150 --> 00:10:13.790
He said in a hadith

00:10:13.790 --> 00:10:14.830
Al-imam Ahmad narrated

00:10:15.550 --> 00:10:17.950
And al-imam al-nasaiyu narrated in his kubara

00:10:17.950 --> 00:10:20.030
By the way al-imam al-nasaiyu

00:10:20.030 --> 00:10:21.470
His sunan is two types

00:10:22.510 --> 00:10:23.870
There's sunan al-kubara

00:10:24.590 --> 00:10:26.430
And there's the one that's called al-mujtaba

00:10:27.390 --> 00:10:29.150
The mujtaba is the sughra

00:10:29.150 --> 00:10:32.430
Scholars dispute was it Nasa'i himself

00:10:33.230 --> 00:10:36.110
Who actually summarized the book

00:10:37.070 --> 00:10:38.910
And he summarized the sunan

00:10:38.910 --> 00:10:40.670
And he made it into his sughra

00:10:41.470 --> 00:10:43.390
And it's the sughra actually from the kubara

00:10:43.390 --> 00:10:44.830
Because there are chapters in the sughra

00:10:44.830 --> 00:10:45.870
That are not in the kubara

00:10:46.750 --> 00:10:48.510
And who was it the person who summarized it?

00:10:48.510 --> 00:10:50.910
There's discussion and dispute that the scholars mentioned

00:10:52.670 --> 00:10:53.790
And when the scholars they say

00:10:53.790 --> 00:10:54.750
Rawahu al-nasaiyu

00:10:54.750 --> 00:10:56.830
Did they actually mean the kubara and not the sughra?

00:10:56.830 --> 00:10:57.950
Or did they mean both?

00:10:57.950 --> 00:10:59.870
What's the istilah of Rawahu al-nasaiyu?

00:10:59.870 --> 00:11:02.110
That's another discussion for another place

00:11:02.590 --> 00:11:03.550
ala kullin

00:11:03.550 --> 00:11:05.150
The place whatever it may be

00:11:05.150 --> 00:11:07.310
Ahmad narrated fee musnadihi in his musnad

00:11:07.870 --> 00:11:10.270
And al-imam al-nasaiyu narrated in his kubara

00:11:10.830 --> 00:11:12.510
That the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:11:12.510 --> 00:11:12.910
He said

00:11:16.910 --> 00:11:18.910
No wealth has benefited me the Prophet said

00:11:19.790 --> 00:11:21.950
The way that the wealth of Abu Bakr benefited me

00:11:22.910 --> 00:11:25.790
Abu Bakr's wealth benefited the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam greatly

00:11:26.590 --> 00:11:27.870
Abu hurayrah narrated this

00:11:28.830 --> 00:11:30.510
From the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:11:32.430 --> 00:11:33.390
With this authentic chain

00:11:34.190 --> 00:11:36.590
Amr ibn al-asir radiya allahu ta'ala anhu he mentioned

00:11:38.030 --> 00:11:38.510
He said

00:11:39.230 --> 00:11:40.270
Amr ibn al-asir said

00:11:40.270 --> 00:11:41.150
Ya rasoola allahi

00:11:41.150 --> 00:11:42.190
O messenger of allah

00:11:42.190 --> 00:11:43.870
Ayyur rijali ahabu ilayka

00:11:43.870 --> 00:11:44.990
Which of the men do you love?

00:11:46.350 --> 00:11:48.350
All of these men that are sitting in front of you

00:11:48.350 --> 00:11:49.630
That you know of

00:11:49.630 --> 00:11:51.550
Who is the most beloved person to you?

00:11:51.550 --> 00:11:53.470
The Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam he said

00:11:53.470 --> 00:11:54.110
Abu Bakr

00:11:55.950 --> 00:11:59.390
Abu Bakr was the most beloved person to the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:12:00.270 --> 00:12:02.990
Al-imam al-tirmidhi authenticated

00:12:03.710 --> 00:12:05.470
From the hadith of Abdullah ibn al-shqeeq

00:12:06.750 --> 00:12:07.390
That he said

00:12:07.390 --> 00:12:08.190
I said to Aisha

00:12:08.190 --> 00:12:09.310
Abdullah ibn al-shqeeq said

00:12:09.310 --> 00:12:10.190
I said to Aisha

00:12:10.990 --> 00:12:12.750
O companions of the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:12:12.750 --> 00:12:15.390
He loved the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:12:16.110 --> 00:12:17.150
Abdullah ibn al-shqeeq

00:12:17.150 --> 00:12:20.110
He asked our mother Aisha radiya allahu wa ta'ala about her

00:12:20.670 --> 00:12:21.470
He said to her

00:12:22.430 --> 00:12:25.550
Which of the companions of the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:12:26.190 --> 00:12:28.590
Was most beloved to the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:12:29.390 --> 00:12:31.390
Aisha without any hesitation she said

00:12:31.390 --> 00:12:32.110
Abu Bakr

00:12:35.950 --> 00:12:38.110
Then he asked her

00:12:38.110 --> 00:12:39.310
Thumma man after that who?

00:12:40.030 --> 00:12:40.750
Qalat Umar

00:12:40.750 --> 00:12:41.390
She said Umar

00:12:42.590 --> 00:12:43.070
Qalat

00:12:43.070 --> 00:12:44.670
Qultu then I said to her after that

00:12:44.670 --> 00:12:45.550
Abdullah ibn al-shqeeq said

00:12:45.550 --> 00:12:46.110
Thumma man

00:12:46.110 --> 00:12:46.830
Who after that?

00:12:47.390 --> 00:12:48.670
Qalat she said

00:12:48.670 --> 00:12:49.630
Abu Ubaidah

00:12:50.670 --> 00:12:51.710
Qultu thumma man

00:12:52.750 --> 00:12:53.710
And then I asked her

00:12:53.710 --> 00:12:54.510
Who after that?

00:12:56.510 --> 00:12:57.150
She went silent

00:12:59.330 --> 00:13:00.690
Aisha radiya allahu wa ta'ala about her

00:13:00.690 --> 00:13:01.570
That's what she mentioned

00:13:03.490 --> 00:13:05.170
Ali radiya allahu wa ta'ala about him

