00:27:53.630 --> 00:27:54.830
If you're not alive

00:27:54.830 --> 00:27:56.270
I don't find you and I can't see you

00:27:56.270 --> 00:27:57.230
What shall I do

00:27:57.230 --> 00:27:57.630
He said

00:27:59.070 --> 00:27:59.950
If you don't find me

00:28:01.470 --> 00:28:02.190
Come to Abu Bakr

00:28:04.990 --> 00:28:07.150
Yeah, and if you can't find me

00:28:07.150 --> 00:28:08.270
Go to Abu Bakr

00:28:08.270 --> 00:28:10.190
Bughari and Muslim both narrated

00:28:10.190 --> 00:28:11.790
Abdullah ibn Mas'ud and he mentioned

00:28:16.590 --> 00:28:17.790
When the Prophet passed away

00:28:19.790 --> 00:28:21.150
Ansar and the Muhajireen

00:28:21.870 --> 00:28:22.830
As you all know

00:28:22.830 --> 00:28:23.390
They thought

00:28:24.350 --> 00:28:25.950
Especially the Ansar

00:28:25.950 --> 00:28:27.070
They thought to themselves

00:28:27.070 --> 00:28:28.430
Now that the Prophet passed away

00:28:28.430 --> 00:28:30.830
We can choose and appoint someone from amongst ourselves

00:28:32.590 --> 00:28:33.070
So they said

00:28:35.150 --> 00:28:37.310
Ansar they said to the Muhajireen

00:28:37.310 --> 00:28:38.910
You guys appoint your own leader

00:28:38.910 --> 00:28:40.350
And we're going to appoint our own leader

00:28:44.030 --> 00:28:44.830
And he said to them

00:28:53.390 --> 00:28:54.910
This is when they went to Bani Saqifa

00:28:54.910 --> 00:28:58.190
They tried to have the Pledge of Allegiance amongst themselves

00:28:58.190 --> 00:28:58.690
Ansar

00:29:01.550 --> 00:29:02.670
They entered onto them

00:29:03.470 --> 00:29:04.590
And Umar spoke to them

00:29:06.350 --> 00:29:07.070
Umar said

00:29:10.350 --> 00:29:10.910
Don't you know

00:29:14.270 --> 00:29:14.910
That the Prophet

00:29:17.310 --> 00:29:19.150
In the Prophet commanded Abu Bakr

00:29:21.150 --> 00:29:22.270
He led the people in the prayer

00:29:23.230 --> 00:29:25.790
Faaayukum tatibu nafsu

00:29:25.790 --> 00:29:28.190
Whose nafs can let him

00:29:30.350 --> 00:29:31.390
To go before Abu Bakr

00:29:31.950 --> 00:29:33.790
Nabila Muhammad appointed Abu Bakr

00:29:33.790 --> 00:29:35.470
As the Imam in the Salah

00:29:35.470 --> 00:29:36.430
The best action

00:29:38.750 --> 00:29:40.190
After the Shahadah attain

00:29:40.190 --> 00:29:41.790
The greatest thing a person can come with

00:29:41.790 --> 00:29:42.510
Is the Salah, right?

00:29:43.550 --> 00:29:45.950
The Prophet entrusted Abu Bakr with the prayer

00:29:45.950 --> 00:29:46.910
And made him the leader

00:29:49.460 --> 00:29:50.580
Who then from amongst you

00:29:50.580 --> 00:29:53.460
Has the audacity and the courage in him

00:29:53.460 --> 00:29:55.460
Or his nafs can even allow him

00:29:55.460 --> 00:29:57.940
And yet taqaddama Aba Bakr to go before Abu Bakr

00:29:58.740 --> 00:29:59.460
Look at the Ansar

00:29:59.460 --> 00:30:00.340
They were righteous people

00:30:00.340 --> 00:30:02.740
Faaqalu na'udhu billahina taqaddama Aba Bakr

00:30:02.740 --> 00:30:03.060
They said

00:30:03.060 --> 00:30:05.300
Wallah we seek refuge in Allah to go before Abu Bakr

00:30:09.330 --> 00:30:09.970
Brothers and sisters

00:30:09.970 --> 00:30:11.090
I'm going to tell you guys a story

00:30:12.130 --> 00:30:13.810
Sahabatun Rasulillahi sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:30:13.810 --> 00:30:14.450
Were human beings

00:30:15.490 --> 00:30:16.370
Our companions

00:30:17.970 --> 00:30:19.650
The companions of the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:30:19.650 --> 00:30:21.970
The companions of the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:30:21.970 --> 00:30:22.610
Were human beings

00:30:22.610 --> 00:30:24.370
Sometimes there was conflicts and

00:30:24.370 --> 00:30:26.690
Disputes and argumentations might happen between them

00:30:27.330 --> 00:30:28.930
But let's look at how they settled it

00:30:30.130 --> 00:30:32.290
I'm going to mention a story of Abu Bakr and Umar

00:30:32.290 --> 00:30:33.890
And a conflict that happened between the two of them

00:30:35.090 --> 00:30:36.850
And Imam al-Bukhari narrated it in Sahih

00:30:36.850 --> 00:30:37.970
From the Hadith of Abu Darda

00:30:39.730 --> 00:30:40.050
He said

00:30:42.450 --> 00:30:44.690
There was between Abu Bakr and Umar

00:30:44.690 --> 00:30:46.210
A discussion and a dialogue

00:30:46.210 --> 00:30:46.930
Something happened

00:30:50.210 --> 00:30:52.850
Abu Bakr must have said something that hurt Abu Bakr

00:30:52.850 --> 00:30:53.730
And Umar got angry

00:30:55.980 --> 00:30:57.420
So Abu Bakr said something

00:30:57.980 --> 00:30:58.940
That angered Umar

00:31:00.380 --> 00:31:01.420
Now Umar what did he do?

00:31:04.220 --> 00:31:05.740
Umar stood up and he got up

00:31:05.740 --> 00:31:08.060
And he just walked away from Abu Bakr

00:31:09.740 --> 00:31:12.060
Then Abu Bakr stood up and he ran after Umar

00:31:12.780 --> 00:31:14.220
And he asked him please forgive me

00:31:14.220 --> 00:31:15.100
I'm sorry what I said

00:31:15.100 --> 00:31:15.740
I shouldn't have said it

00:31:17.420 --> 00:31:19.500
Umar ignored Abu Bakr

00:31:19.500 --> 00:31:20.780
He went into his house and he locked

00:31:20.780 --> 00:31:21.500
He closed his door

00:31:21.500 --> 00:31:25.340
And he slammed the door on the face of Abu Bakr

00:31:27.100 --> 00:31:28.460
Ignored what he said

00:31:28.460 --> 00:31:31.900
He got the door and he slammed it in the face of Abu Bakr

00:31:32.860 --> 00:31:33.820
Brothers and sisters

00:31:34.860 --> 00:31:38.220
A discussion happened between the two of them

00:31:39.340 --> 00:31:42.220
Abu Bakr said something that upset Umar

00:31:42.220 --> 00:31:43.100
Umar got angry

00:31:44.540 --> 00:31:46.700
As soon as Umar stood up and walked off

00:31:46.700 --> 00:31:49.180
Abu Bakr got after him and ran after him

00:31:50.140 --> 00:31:51.980
Look at the manners of the Sahabas

00:31:51.980 --> 00:31:53.340
And how conflict was settled

00:31:55.380 --> 00:31:56.980
Umar ignored Abu Bakr

00:31:56.980 --> 00:31:57.780
He's furious

00:31:57.780 --> 00:31:58.580
He's angry

00:31:59.300 --> 00:32:01.460
But he doesn't say a word of disrespect to Abu Bakr

00:32:02.020 --> 00:32:03.140
Because that's his senior

00:32:03.140 --> 00:32:04.420
It's his older brother

00:32:04.420 --> 00:32:05.460
But he's angry with him

00:32:06.900 --> 00:32:08.260
So Umar what he does

00:32:08.260 --> 00:32:10.100
He goes into his house and he closes the door

00:32:10.660 --> 00:32:12.500
Now Abu Bakr can't enter the house of Umar

00:32:12.500 --> 00:32:13.300
Without his permission

00:32:13.300 --> 00:32:14.900
And Umar has not given him the permission

00:32:16.260 --> 00:32:17.300
Brothers and sisters

00:32:17.300 --> 00:32:18.820
We ponder and we contemplate here

00:32:18.820 --> 00:32:19.380
And we think

00:32:20.180 --> 00:32:21.220
Abu Bakr didn't say

00:32:21.220 --> 00:32:22.420
Oh well I tried my best

00:32:22.420 --> 00:32:24.660
You didn't want to accept my forgiveness

00:32:24.660 --> 00:32:25.700
And he didn't walk away

00:32:25.700 --> 00:32:26.200
Wallah

00:32:27.060 --> 00:32:28.740
He thought what can I possibly do

00:32:29.460 --> 00:32:30.980
To get the forgiveness of my brother

00:32:33.150 --> 00:32:34.190
Abu Bakr thought

00:32:34.910 --> 00:32:36.030
He said to himself

00:32:36.030 --> 00:32:37.310
What can I possibly do

00:32:38.430 --> 00:32:40.030
To get the forgiveness of my brother

00:32:40.030 --> 00:32:40.750
I've wronged him

00:32:40.750 --> 00:32:41.950
I've said something that upset him

00:32:41.950 --> 00:32:42.830
He got angry

00:32:42.830 --> 00:32:44.590
I tried to ask him for forgiveness

00:32:44.590 --> 00:32:45.950
He didn't accept it

00:32:45.950 --> 00:32:47.710
What can I possibly do

00:32:47.710 --> 00:32:50.830
That could insha'Allah make him forgive me

00:32:51.870 --> 00:32:53.070
He said if I go to the Prophet

00:32:53.630 --> 00:32:54.990
And I speak to the Prophet

00:32:54.990 --> 00:32:57.630
Maybe the Prophet can influence Abu Umar

00:32:57.630 --> 00:32:58.270
To forgive me

00:32:59.470 --> 00:33:01.470
So Abu Bakr went to the Prophet

00:33:01.470 --> 00:33:03.630
Sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:33:03.630 --> 00:33:05.070
The Messenger Sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:33:05.070 --> 00:33:06.590
When he saw Abu Bakr from far

00:33:07.790 --> 00:33:08.350
The Prophet

00:33:08.350 --> 00:33:10.110
The Prophet was sitting with his companions

00:33:10.110 --> 00:33:12.110
And he saw from Abu Bakr walking from far

00:33:12.110 --> 00:33:12.670
He could see him

00:33:12.670 --> 00:33:14.910
Sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:33:14.910 --> 00:33:15.870
And then the Prophet

00:33:15.870 --> 00:33:17.070
Because he knows Abu Bakr

00:33:17.070 --> 00:33:19.470
The same way Abu Bakr knew the Prophet deeply

00:33:19.470 --> 00:33:20.670
And studied the Prophet

00:33:20.670 --> 00:33:22.910
The Prophet was like that to Abu Bakr as well

00:33:22.910 --> 00:33:23.710
The Prophet

00:33:23.710 --> 00:33:25.230
And Abu Bakr had a very strong bond

00:33:25.950 --> 00:33:27.390
So when the Prophet saw him from far

00:33:27.390 --> 00:33:28.190
The Prophet said

00:33:28.190 --> 00:33:28.510
He said

00:33:28.510 --> 00:33:30.670
Amma sahibukum hadha faghad ghamar

00:33:31.390 --> 00:33:32.670
He said as your

00:33:32.670 --> 00:33:34.430
He stood with the companions of the Prophet

00:33:34.430 --> 00:33:37.150
He said as for your friend

00:33:37.150 --> 00:33:38.030
And Abu Bakr

00:33:38.750 --> 00:33:41.230
Faghad ghamara means he went into a discussion

00:33:41.230 --> 00:33:42.350
A heated discussion

00:33:42.350 --> 00:33:43.870
And something went wrong in that discussion

00:33:43.870 --> 00:33:44.510
The Prophet said

00:33:46.720 --> 00:33:47.680
Ya'ni he's upset

00:33:48.160 --> 00:33:48.800
Umar today

00:33:48.800 --> 00:33:51.200
Abu Bakr's face does not look like he's pleased

00:33:51.200 --> 00:33:53.120
Something has upset Abu Bakr

00:33:53.120 --> 00:33:53.840
The Prophet said

00:33:57.100 --> 00:33:58.140
Abu Dardak mentioned

00:34:00.540 --> 00:34:02.380
Now Abu Bakr is walking to the Prophet

00:34:02.380 --> 00:34:03.260
Alayhi salatu wa salam

00:34:04.700 --> 00:34:06.700
Umar at home thinks about what he did

00:34:07.260 --> 00:34:10.060
How he closed the door in front of his brother Abu Bakr

00:34:10.060 --> 00:34:11.580
Look at the bond between these Sahabahs

00:34:11.580 --> 00:34:12.780
Sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:34:12.780 --> 00:34:13.980
There's a lot we can learn from it

00:34:16.900 --> 00:34:18.260
Umar he realized he said

00:34:18.260 --> 00:34:19.780
I have upset my brother

00:34:20.660 --> 00:34:22.260
I have hurt my brother

00:34:22.420 --> 00:34:23.700
And I shouldn't have done that

00:34:23.700 --> 00:34:24.980
He asked for my forgiveness

00:34:24.980 --> 00:34:26.020
And I should have accepted it

00:34:26.900 --> 00:34:27.540
So he got up

00:34:28.260 --> 00:34:29.300
And he went out of his house

00:34:30.100 --> 00:34:31.620
And he came to the house of Abu Bakr

00:34:32.260 --> 00:34:34.020
When he came to the house of Abu Bakr

00:34:34.580 --> 00:34:36.500
He was told that Abu Bakr is not here

00:34:37.220 --> 00:34:38.260
And as soon as he was told

00:34:38.260 --> 00:34:39.140
Abu Bakr is not here

00:34:39.140 --> 00:34:40.500
He knew where Abu Bakr would be

00:34:41.060 --> 00:34:41.620
So he said

00:34:41.620 --> 00:34:42.500
I'm going to go to the Prophet

00:34:42.500 --> 00:34:43.300
Alayhi salatu wa salam

00:34:46.480 --> 00:34:48.240
As for Abu Bakr

00:34:49.120 --> 00:34:50.160
He came to the Prophet

00:34:50.160 --> 00:34:51.680
Sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:34:52.400 --> 00:34:53.600
And then he told the Prophet

00:34:53.600 --> 00:34:54.640
Alayhi salatu wa salam

00:34:55.520 --> 00:34:56.800
What took place and what happened

00:34:59.340 --> 00:35:01.100
As soon as Abu Bakr told

00:35:01.100 --> 00:35:02.700
The Prophet Sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:35:02.700 --> 00:35:04.140
What happened between him and Umar

00:35:05.180 --> 00:35:05.900
Look what happened

00:35:06.620 --> 00:35:08.940
The narration he mentions

00:35:08.940 --> 00:35:11.100
Fa ghadiba Rasululayhi salallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:35:11.100 --> 00:35:12.300
Another narration mentions

00:35:12.300 --> 00:35:14.220
Fata ma'ara wajwa Rasululayhi salallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:35:14.220 --> 00:35:16.700
The Prophet's face changed

00:35:16.700 --> 00:35:18.700
Alayhi salatu wa salam

00:35:18.700 --> 00:35:20.220
The Prophet became very angry

00:35:20.220 --> 00:35:21.180
Alayhi salatu wa salam

00:35:22.220 --> 00:35:23.820
Wa ja'ala Abu Bakrin yaqul

00:35:24.540 --> 00:35:25.740
Abu Bakr kept saying

00:35:26.220 --> 00:35:27.580
Wallahi ya Rasulallah

00:35:27.580 --> 00:35:28.380
O Messenger of Allah

00:35:31.260 --> 00:35:32.300
I was the one who wronged him

00:35:32.300 --> 00:35:33.420
I was the one who oppressed him

00:35:34.700 --> 00:35:36.380
Another rivaia mentions

00:35:36.380 --> 00:35:38.540
That Abu Bakr was standing

00:35:38.540 --> 00:35:40.620
And when he saw the Prophet's face change

00:35:40.620 --> 00:35:42.140
Fajatha ala rukbatayhi

00:35:42.140 --> 00:35:43.580
Fell on his knees on the ground

00:35:43.580 --> 00:35:44.060
And then he said

00:35:44.060 --> 00:35:44.700
Ya Rasulallah

00:35:44.700 --> 00:35:45.980
I was the one who wronged him

00:35:45.980 --> 00:35:46.940
It wasn't Umar's fault

00:35:48.620 --> 00:35:50.140
But the Prophet Sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:35:50.140 --> 00:35:51.340
Had didn't listen to Abu Bakr

00:35:52.620 --> 00:35:54.380
And the Prophet waited for Umar to come

00:35:54.940 --> 00:35:56.220
And as soon as Umar reached

00:35:57.180 --> 00:35:59.340
And the face of the Prophet Sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:35:59.340 --> 00:36:00.060
Fully changed

00:36:00.780 --> 00:36:02.300
The Prophet said the following to Umar

00:36:02.300 --> 00:36:03.740
And to all of the companions

00:36:04.300 --> 00:36:05.980
Something that changed

00:36:05.980 --> 00:36:08.140
The entire companions

00:36:08.140 --> 00:36:10.060
The way they looked at Abu Bakr

00:36:10.060 --> 00:36:11.340
The Prophet said to them all

00:36:13.820 --> 00:36:15.260
Are you not going to leave my friend for me?

00:36:16.140 --> 00:36:17.580
The Prophet is talking to Abu Bakr

00:36:18.220 --> 00:36:19.260
He's talking to Uthman

00:36:19.260 --> 00:36:20.140
He's talking to Ali

00:36:20.940 --> 00:36:22.220
He's talking to Khalid min Walid

00:36:22.220 --> 00:36:23.340
He's talking to Ashraf al Mubashirin

00:36:23.660 --> 00:36:24.620
All of them are sitting there

00:36:25.340 --> 00:36:26.460
And the Prophet said to them

00:36:29.660 --> 00:36:31.500
Are you guys not going to leave my friend for me?

00:36:32.460 --> 00:36:34.540
As though the rest are not companions

00:36:34.540 --> 00:36:37.660
As though the rest are not his sahib

00:36:38.780 --> 00:36:41.020
We refer to all the other sahabahs

00:36:41.020 --> 00:36:42.140
The companions of the Prophet

00:36:43.100 --> 00:36:43.980
But the Prophet said

00:36:46.780 --> 00:36:48.540
Are you not going to leave my friend alone for me?

00:36:49.900 --> 00:36:51.740
And then the Prophet reminded them something

00:36:53.340 --> 00:36:54.060
The Prophet said

00:36:57.980 --> 00:36:58.700
The Prophet said

00:36:58.700 --> 00:37:00.060
I said to all of you guys

00:37:00.060 --> 00:37:01.260
All of you guys here

00:37:01.260 --> 00:37:02.300
And unto Quraish

00:37:04.940 --> 00:37:06.300
I said to all of you people

00:37:07.020 --> 00:37:07.660
O people

00:37:10.220 --> 00:37:12.940
I am a messenger sent from Allah to all of you

00:37:15.260 --> 00:37:16.860
All of you guys said to me you're a liar

00:37:19.140 --> 00:37:20.660
All of you guys disbelieved in me

00:37:22.900 --> 00:37:24.740
Abu Bakr was the only man who said to me

00:37:25.300 --> 00:37:26.020
You told the truth

00:37:27.300 --> 00:37:29.940
He believed me at a time when none of you believed in me

00:37:29.940 --> 00:37:31.060
He chose to believe in me

00:37:33.760 --> 00:37:34.720
The Prophet also said

00:37:39.760 --> 00:37:42.160
He helped me and he aided me through his family

00:37:42.880 --> 00:37:43.600
And his wealth

00:37:43.600 --> 00:37:44.400
He gave me everything

00:37:47.360 --> 00:37:49.520
Abu Darda mentioned in that narration

00:37:50.320 --> 00:37:51.840
From that day onwards

00:37:53.280 --> 00:37:55.520
No one ever dared to speak back to Abu Bakr

00:37:56.400 --> 00:37:57.040
No one dared

00:37:57.040 --> 00:37:58.640
Abu Bakr reached that level

00:38:04.300 --> 00:38:05.100
At that level

00:38:05.100 --> 00:38:06.220
The Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:38:06.220 --> 00:38:07.340
He said in another narration

00:38:08.860 --> 00:38:10.540
Every single one of you

00:38:10.540 --> 00:38:12.300
The Prophet said to his companions

00:38:12.300 --> 00:38:14.380
Every single one of you sitting here

00:38:15.340 --> 00:38:16.540
Whatever you've done for me

00:38:16.540 --> 00:38:17.740
I've done for you in return

00:38:18.540 --> 00:38:19.580
I've repaid you back

00:38:22.960 --> 00:38:23.280
He said

00:38:26.720 --> 00:38:27.680
Only Abu Bakr

00:38:32.380 --> 00:38:32.780
He said

00:38:33.820 --> 00:38:34.620
Only Abu Bakr

00:38:36.380 --> 00:38:38.460
I have left Allah to reward him

00:38:38.460 --> 00:38:39.420
I can't too much

00:38:39.420 --> 00:38:40.540
What Abu Bakr has done for me

00:38:45.900 --> 00:38:46.300
He said

00:39:03.020 --> 00:39:04.460
When Abu Bakr was appointed

00:39:04.460 --> 00:39:05.340
The Muslim leader

00:39:05.340 --> 00:39:06.540
And he was made in charge

00:39:07.980 --> 00:39:09.180
He used to go to the market

00:39:09.180 --> 00:39:09.820
Abu Bakr

00:39:10.380 --> 00:39:11.500
And there were thobes

00:39:11.500 --> 00:39:12.700
That he had on his shoulders

00:39:13.580 --> 00:39:14.460
Ya'ni Cloths

00:39:15.500 --> 00:39:16.620
He had on his shoulders

00:39:17.500 --> 00:39:19.020
And he was making money

00:39:19.580 --> 00:39:21.500
He's the khalif of the Muslims

00:39:21.500 --> 00:39:22.940
The leader of the Muslims

00:39:22.940 --> 00:39:24.060
He wanted to make money

00:39:24.780 --> 00:39:25.580
For his family

00:39:26.220 --> 00:39:28.060
It wasn't using the wealth of the Muslims

00:39:28.940 --> 00:39:30.540
So Umar and Abu Ubaidah

00:39:31.100 --> 00:39:32.780
Two people who were promised general life

00:39:32.780 --> 00:39:34.460
They saw Abu Bakr in this situation

00:39:36.540 --> 00:39:37.260
They spoke to him

00:39:37.900 --> 00:39:38.220
